GodlyItems = ["**Batteries**: Power any electronic item! (Will eventually run out depending on item's power consumption.)", "**Thanksgiving Feast**: One-use. Fully heals the entire party.", "**Imagination Potion**: Bring your imagination to life. Drains 1 Imagination point on each use.", "**Baseball Slinger**: A ranged weapon using baseballs as ammo. 4 base damage. Fires them *very fast*.", "**Overclocker:** One-use. Can be applied to any consumable item; when used, that item's max uses increases by 1.","**HOG for President Pin**: Gives the wearer +1 in all stats and raises health 25% (round down if decimal occurs). Also, this pin pisses off anyone named JOG. Not a power this item has, just an observation and truth.", "**Needle of Loyalty**: One use. Stabbing any NPC with this needle causes them to get mind controlled and join the party. Lasts for two worlds; the NPC will not be happy when the effect wears off.", "**Lightsaber**: A base 12 damage weapon. Overuse will wear out its batteries.", "**The Magic Flute**: A ranged weapon with base 95 damage. When played, the magic flute will vaporize any being it does enough damage to kill. Cannot be used by any character without the Musician trait.", "**Voodoo Dice**: Whenever the player uses this item, any bad roll can be given to another player for their next turn, and this player can reroll. If the dice are ever destroyed, stolen, or lost, the player who was using this item has all stats drop to 0 and health reduced to 1. When this occurs, every other player also recieves stat boosts equal to the stat reduction of their companion distributed over the entire party. To summarize, if a player acquires this item, get ready to have the party turn against one another.", "**Blob-Be-Gone Hose:** This hose squirts a magical substance that is completely harmless unless you are either a giant Green Blob or a giant Pink Blob. If this hose is used to attack either a giant Green Blob or a giant Pink Blob, the Blob dissolves and dies. Woohoo!", "**Beethoven‚Äôs unfinished Tenth Symphony:** If the player finds it and completes it, Beethoven appears and rewards the player with the magic flute and music lessons that gain the player the Musician trait. Doing so requires a Smartness check with a base modifier of -18.", "**Space Ripper**: Allows the party to immediately travel to any world on the map. As long as they do not select a repeat world, this can be used to change the El Dorado route significantly. The selected world will still count as the next world.", "**Steroids**: Increases Strongness by 5. It is illegal to use these and then participate in an athletic competition.", "**Lightning Rod**: Allows Lightning to be cast from any distance, dealing a 150 base damage ranged attack. Requires Electromancer to use. Has a 1 in 20 chance to give anyone struck with it Electromancer."] #20
GreatItems = ["**Spicy Taco Surprise**: A base 25 damage explosive. You can probably trick dumb people into eating this.","**GoFundMe Starter Kit**: Allows the user to start a virtual campaign on the site GoFundMe. If they pass a coolness check, they will receive a random amount of gold between 0 and 300.", "**Shield**: When in your inventory, reduces all damage taken by 2.", "**Pickpocket Machine**: One-use. Allows you to steal one item from someone else's inventory. Does not work on bosses.", "**Cell Battery**: Power any electronic item for one use!", "**Mind Reader**: Reads the minds of anyone within five feet. Requires batteries.", "**Staple Gun of the Moon**: A weapon that fires staples as ammo. 1 base damage. Allows ranged attacking.", "**Age Changer**: Change your age on demand!", "**Item Spawner**: Spawns two random items once per world.", "**Chainsaw**: Requires batteries. 16 base damage weapon.", "**Mouth Stealer**: Ranged weapon that can be used once on every person. 9 base damage. When used,the person's mouth is removed and they can no longer speak.", "**Set of Explosive Nesting Dolls**: Although this weapon appears to just be a regular set of Nesting Dolls, each doll that is a part of this set can act as a powerful grenade. The set comes with 5 dolls which must be used in order; they have 32 base damage, 16 base damage, 8 base damage, 4 base damage, and 2 base damage respectively.", "**Yoga Mat**: Allows you to perform a yoga routine, increasing your Strongness by 2.", "**Trading Machine**: Allows you to exchange any inventory item for the inventory item of an NPC. Requires batteries.", "**Lightsaber minus Batteries**: A base 1 damage weapon. Electrical power will power it up to base 12.", "**Magic Lottery Ticket:** This lottery ticket contains 9 boxes which can be scratched off to obtain X amount of gold. Eight of the boxes are helpful and will give you between 50 and 5000 gold. One box, however, will curse the player that uses this item! The cursed player's stats all instantly reduced to 2/2/2 (the person who made this lottery ticket is sadistic, but not 100% cruel). After a player is cursed, the item becomes useless. If the cursed box is somehow the final box remaining and the player is stupid enough to attempt to use it, a roll is made to determine its effect. If a 10 or lower is rolled, the players stats are reduced to 0/0/0 AND the entire party, not just the cursed player, lose all gold they have on hand. If an 11 or higher is rolled, the cursed player is in the 1%! Gold the player currently has is doubled AND stats are increased by +7/+7/+7.", "**Communist Manifesto**: Reading this book increases Smartness by 3 and replaces your first trait with Communist.", "**Kidz Bop Radio Speaker 5000:** This is a weapon with 5 base damage, surprisingly! The con of this item is the terrible music you are subjecting your enemies to. Comes with earplugs to protect the party.", "**Pendant of Willpower**: Allows one reroll per world while equipped. Only one pendant can be worn at once.", "**Chili's All You Can Eat Coupon:** If you can get this to Chili's, you are going to get so much food.", "**Mace and Chain:** Requires 9 Strongness to hold. 10 base damage melee weapon.", "**Timey-Wimey Stick**: Forcibly time travels anyone who is hit with it to a random point in the future. Has a 50% chance to break on each use.", "**Wooden Stake**: 1 base damage against normal enemies. 100 base damage against enemies with the Vampire trait.", "**Rights to Friends**: This item has a one time use where you can exchange the item to get rid of any NPC instantly without conflict. This does not include boss fights.", "**Heaven's Blade**: Has a 50% chance to restore 77 points of health and has a 50% chance to deal exactly 77 points of damage."] #16 to 19G
